## Summary
This documentation page explains how to test guides and surveys in Amplitude using Preview mode, which allows developers to verify conditions, settings, and behavior before launching. It details how to enter preview mode, understand condition statuses, troubleshoot preview issues, and conduct live testing with targeted cohorts.

